{"type": "article", "id": 11911, "title": "木制滑板", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-10T11:30:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000054jydT0OwXtPGvbCzF.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t今天的第二件作品也同样取材自大自然，这是 Woody Skateboards 推出的木制滑板，木材全部来自乌得勒支和阿姆斯特丹，团队利用城市建设工程中废弃的木材，打造了一个个精致的滑板，这些木材上面印了它们详细的年龄，品种和生长地等信息。相信拿到滑板的会像得到一个朋友一样对待这些充满生命力的滑板。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135855kuvCFNMcp1zbx3mW.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261358563eTQo5gw8ZxG4q69.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135857mgNhAcOL0WfbXC7i.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"460\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}